    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，C1触发C2，用axios发POST请求到/interpretar路径。然后这边有个关键设计——我们用了Vite做代理，P1会把/api开头的请求转发到localhost:3001。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C2",
