    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。S1收到之后交给S2做parser，生成AST。然后S3是解释器核心，负责执行这个AST。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
